The Police Command in Oyo State has confirmed the killing of Mrs. Olayemi Grace Odetomi by gunmen. She was the wife of Peter Oluremi Odetomi, a former Commissioner for Local Government and Chieftancy Matters. Odetomi was shot dead on Friday in her residence at Ashi in the Bodija area of Ibadan, the state capital. Police Public Relations Officer, DSP Adewale Osifeso, confirmed the incident. The spokesman said the deceased died immediately after being shot. Osifeso assured that further updates will be communicated to the public.